## 💬 Common Interview Q&A

### ❓ _How do you increase dump retention?_

> - Schedule report **`RSSNAPDL`** with a _custom retention period_
> - **_OR_** adjust the profile parameter **`rsdb/snp_lifetime`** _(value in seconds)_

---

### ❓ _How do you handle a **`TIME_OUT`** dump?_

> 1. Check if **_program logic_** can be optimized _(first priority)_
> 2. Run the program in **background mode** _(longer timeout: **3600s** vs 600s)_
> 3. As a ***last resort***, increase `rdisp/max_wprun_time`
>
> ⚠️ _Increasing `rdisp/max_wprun_time` is <ins>not recommended</ins> as a permanent fix — it affects **all** dialog processes._

---

### ❓ _How do you handle **`TSV_TNEW_PAGE_ALLOC_FAILED`**?_

> Check and tune these **_memory parameters_**:
>
> | Parameter | Controls |
> |---|---|
> | **`abap/heap_area_dia`** | Max heap per _dialog_ work process |
> | **`abap/heap_area_nondia`** | Max heap per _non-dialog_ work process |
> | **`em/initial_size_MB`** | ***Extended memory*** pool size |
> | **`ztta/roll_area`** | _Roll area_ per work process |
>
> _Also, ask the **ABAP developer** to optimize the program's memory consumption._

---

### ❓ _How do you proactively monitor dumps?_

> - ✅ Check **ST22** _daily_ as part of **_daily monitoring checklist_**
> - ✅ Set up **CCMS alerts** via **`RZ20`** for _automatic notifications_
> - ✅ Use ***Solution Manager*** for <ins>centralized monitoring</ins> across systems
> - ✅ Create a **_custom Z-report_** to email dump summaries to the Basis team

---

### ❓ _How do you analyze a short dump step by step?_

> 1. Open **ST22** → Select the dump by _date & time_
> 2. Read the **_"What Happened"_** section for a summary
> 3. Check the **_"How to Correct"_** section for SAP's recommendation
> 4. Review the ***source code*** section to find the exact failing line
> 5. Examine the **_call stack_** to understand the execution flow
> 6. Note the **user**, **program**, and **timestamp** for further investigation

---

### ❓ _What is the difference between ST22 and SM21?_

> | Feature | **ST22** | **SM21** |
> |---|---|---|
> | **Purpose** | _ABAP runtime errors_ (short dumps) | _System log_ (all system events) |
> | **Scope** | Only **_program crashes_** | **Warnings**, errors, _login failures_, system messages |
> | **Used By** | Basis + ***ABAP Developers*** | Primarily **_Basis Admins_** |
> | **Detail Level** | <ins>Very detailed</ins> — code level | _High level_ — event log |

